{"tid":914407,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"內地《王者榮耀》網紅主播嗨氏跳槽毀約　被判罰半億違約金","createTime":"2018-11-24T08:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T08:52:00.000Z","uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7d6140e4143d41cbe4f9ad28bd24b2f8294d33","tid":914407,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:47:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ezoneclub/posts/10156784085195050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fezoneclub%2Fposts%2F10156784085195050&d=jvvzT6rx31Fn0FjFXWvslUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=67d45ea5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ezoneclub/posts/10156784085195050</a><br />\n內地直播平台競爭激烈，各平台除了互搶觀眾外，亦會互搶知名網紅主播坐陣。大陸知名《王者榮耀》網紅主播嗨氏（江海濤），透過直播打機成名，甚至被稱為「《王者榮耀》第一人」。他在 2017 年 8 月從虎牙直播跳槽至鬥魚直播，被虎牙直播控告違約。該違約事件早前已在一審法院中，判決虎牙直播勝訴，嗨氏需要各虎牙直播支付 4,900 萬人民幣（折合約 5,518 萬港元）違約金。嗨氏不服一審判決，提出上訴。最近在廣州中院為違約事件進行二審判決，駁回嗨氏的上訴，維持原判。<br />\n=========<br />\n成半個億，唔知達哥搵唔搵到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b7538c221a4bfadfa00453762384f16196c3e2","tid":914407,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:49:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2215756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2215756&d=jvvzT6rx31Fn0FjFXWvslUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=43893bd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2215756</a>"},{